org.afplib.afplib

Interface CPD

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CPDImpl

    public interface CPD
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'CPD'.

    The following features are supported:

    • CP Desc
    • GCGID Len
    • Num Cd Pts
    • GCSGID
    • CPGID
    • Enc Scheme

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getCPD()
